+chesscoin_backend    | {"level":"error","message":"[[Start] Fatal:] Can't reach database server at `pgbouncer:5432`\n\nPlease make sure your database server is running at `pgbouncer:5432`.","stack":"PrismaClientInitializationError: Can't reach database server at `pgbouncer:5432`\n\nPlease make sure your database server is running at `pgbouncer:5432`.\n    at t (/app/node_modules/@prisma/client/runtime/library.js:112:2488)\n    at async start (/app/dist/index.js:151:9)","timestamp":"2026-04-11 22:58:21"}
+chesscoin_backend    | [Redis] Connected
+chesscoin_backend    | [Redis] Connected
+chesscoin_backend    | [Redis] Connected
+chesscoin_backend    | [Redis] Keyspace notifications enabled
+chesscoin_backend    | {"level":"info","message":"[Socket.io] Redis adapter enabled","timestamp":"2026-04-11 22:58:22"}
+chesscoin_frontend   | /docker-entrypoint.sh: /docker-entrypoint.d/ is not empty, will attempt to perform 
+
+Что исправить:
+1. **docker-compose.yml** — добавить зависимость между сервисами:
+   ```yaml
+   services:
+     backend:
+       depends_on:
+         pgbouncer:
+           condition: service_healthy
+   ```
+
+2. **docker-compose.yml** — добавить healthcheck для pgbouncer:
+   ```yaml
+   services:
+     pgbouncer:
+       healthcheck:
+         test: ["CMD", "pg_isready", "-h", "localhost", "-p", "6432"]
+         interval: 5s
+         timeout: 3s
+         retries: 5
+   ```
+
+3. **backend/Dockerfile** — добавить ожидание БД перед запуском:
+   ```dockerfile
+   # Добавить wait-for-it или использовать healthcheck
+   COPY wait-for-it.sh /wait-for-it.sh
+   RUN chmod +x /wait-for-it.sh
+   CMD ["/wait-for-it.sh", "pgbouncer:6432", "--", "npm", "start"]
+   ```
+
+4. **backend/src/index.ts** (или точка входа) — увеличить таймаут подключения Prisma:
+   ```typescript
+   const prisma = new PrismaClient({
+     datasources: {
+       db: {
+         url: process.env.DATABASE_URL
+       }
+     },
+     // Добавить:
+     __internal: {
+       engine: {
+         enableConnectionTimeout: false
+       }
+     }
+   })
+   ```
+
+5. **.env** (или переменные окружения backend) — проверить DATABASE_URL:
+   ```
+   DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:pass@pgbouncer:6432/dbname?pgbouncer=true
+   ```
+
+6. **docker-compose.yml** — убедиться, что pgbouncer слушает на порту 5432 внутри сети:
+   ```yaml
+   pgbouncer:
+     ports:
+       - "5432:5432"  # или "6432:6432" если используется порт 6432
+   ```
+
+7. **pgbouncer/pgbouncer.ini** — проверить конфигурацию:
+   ```
+   listen_port = 5432
+   listen_addr = *
+   auth_type = md5
+   auth_file = /etc/pgbouncer/userlist.txt

